# Documentation

- Keep `docs/progress.md` updated when completing milestones.
- Record architectural decisions in `docs/decisions.md` (ADR format: Context, Decision, Consequences).
- `docs/next-task.md` should always reflect the single next actionable task.
- Link to relevant files and migrations when documenting schema changes in `docs/database.md`.
